amond; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">Glencore</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline"> Xstrata</span></a></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Ed Daniels, Chairman of Shell UK Limited, </span><a href="http://data.parliament.uk/writtenevidence/WrittenEvidence.svc/EvidencePdf/2721"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">Shell International Limited</span></a></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Tara Hopkins, Chief Adviser, External Affairs, Europe</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">, </span><a href="http://data.parliament.uk/writtenevidence/WrittenEvidence.svc/EvidencePdf/2607"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">Rio Tinto</span></a></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:justify"><a href="http://www.parliamentlive.tv/Main/Player.aspx?meetingId=14298"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">Watch the meeting</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Members present: </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Mr Adrian Bailey (Chair)</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">; </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Mr William Bain</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">; </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-