ause us enormous problems </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">i</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">n making decisions on investments.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Charles </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Watenphul</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: To follow on from Tara’s point, our footprint in the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> is limited to a relatively small zinc/lead smelter, called Britannia, down in </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Kent</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Chair:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> Sorry, can you speak up?</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Some of us are getting old and hard of hearing.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Charles </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Watenphul</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: My apologies.</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Our operations in the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> are limited to on